data.description:
Ranch style, 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathrooms with almost 5 ACRES! 

You definitely don't see properties like this lately.

This ready to move in home has roomy bedrooms, beautiful floors, freshly painted walls and you have to appreciate the amount of kitchen storage it has to offer! Not to mention 5 acres of partially wooded area for you to enjoy!

Located 5 minutes from The Lakes Mall and a ton of surrounding shops and restaurants in Norton Shores.
20 minutes to downtown Grand Haven, 20 minutes to downtown Muskegon and 20 minutes to Lake Michigan. 
This home puts you in the center of so many wonderful locations and experiences. 

Set up a showing to come see your new home today!
